ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=kazuya
 _erdos@brown.edu;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:kazuya_erdos@brown.edu
CREATED:20230108T172841Z
DESCRIPTION:Hi Kazuya Erdos\,\n\nThank you for picking a time for our inter
 view. Please be sure to accept the calendar invitation and note the time zo
 ne. Our interview will be conducted using Zoom with cameras turned on. The 
 interview could take approximately one hour and will be recorded. Please ma
 ke arrangements to be in an area with strong connection and where we may sp
 eak without background noise interference. I look forward to speaking with 
 you soon. \n\nBest Regards\, \n\nPaulina Romero\n\n________________________
 ___________________\n\nPREPARE FOR INTERVIEW:  \n\n1) Test Zoom using detai
 ls below. You should be able to share your screen. First time using Zoom? Y
 ou may be asked to download the free Zoom app before connecting. \n\n2) Fam
 iliarize yourself with the Instructor job description on our On-Campus Jobs
  page (https://www.idtech.com/jobs/employment-in-person) \n\n3) Review the 
 courses offered at the locations (https://www.idtech.com/on-campus) you sel
 ected in your application and be ready to discuss what you're able to teach
 .\n\n4) For the teaching demo portion of the interview\, please prepare the
  following in advance:\n\n* Intro (approx 1 min): Introduce yourself as an 
 iD Tech instructor\n* Icebreaker (approx 2-3 min): Play a brief game or ice
 breaker\n* Expectations (approx 2-3 min): Set behavioral expectations for t
 he class\n* Brief Lesson (approx 5 min): Teach a brief lesson on a subject 
 you are comfortable with and that we offer at our on-campus programs (https
 ://www.idtech.com/courses) . Be sure to include a lesson recap at the end.\
 n\n___________________________________________  \n\nZOOM DETAILS: Location:
  This is a Zoom web conference.\n\nYou can join this meeting from your comp
 uter\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://idtech-co.zoom.us/j/96150126696\n\n
 One tap mobile:\n+1 301 715 8592\,\,96150126696#\n+1 305 224 1968\,\,961501
 26696#\n\nYou can also dial in using your phone.\nUS: +1 301 715 8592\, +1 
 305 224 1968\, +1 309 205 3325\, +1 312 626 6799\, +1 646 931 3860\, +1 929
  436 2866\, +1 360 209 5623\, +1 386 347 5053\, +1 507 473 4847\, +1 564 21
 7 2000\, +1 669 444 9171\, +1 669 900 6833\, +16892781000\, +1 719 359 4580
 \, +1 253 205 0468\, +1 253 215 8782\, +1 346 248 7799\nMeeting ID: 961-501
 -26696\n\nFind your local number: https://idtech-co.zoom.us/u/aUcCPToKy\n \
 n\n___________________________________________\n\nNEED TO CANCEL or RESCHED
 ULE?\n\nReschedule Reason: Commuting back to college campus \n\nNeed to mak
 e changes to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/68a04b
 94-4a49-4ebc-92dc-78eb1217c3f2\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/rescheduli
 ngs/68a04b94-4a49-4ebc-92dc-78eb1217c3f2\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20230122T235311Z
LOCATION:https://idtech-co.zoom.us/j/96150126696
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kazuya Erdos - Instructor Interview with Paulina Romero
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
