CREATED:20230428T151339Z
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars! The 8th Annual Brown CS Undergrad Research
  Symposium is just around the corner\, and we would love to see you there.\
 n  \n  Event Info\n  The Undergraduate CS Research Symposium is an exciting
  opportunity for undergraduates to present their computer science-related r
 esearch to fellow students\, faculty judges\, and industry partners. There 
 will be a poster session\, free food\, swag\, and a chance to win cash priz
 es!\n  \n  Date and Time: Tues\, May 2nd\, 4-7pm ET\n  Location: CIT 3rd fl
 oor Atrium\n  RSVP: https://forms.gle/iMDCg6ioBHCpfSMh7\n  Facebook Event: 
 https://fb.me/e/NxDSMwp2\n  \n  Prizes\n  Brown Undergrad Awards: $400 (1st
  Place)\, $300 (2nd Place)\, $200 (3rd Place)\n  Audience Favorites: $100 (
 2 projects)\n  Raffle: Brown University’s very own CS department swag\n  \n
   If you are interested in presenting\, here is the (very short and editabl
 e!) abstract submission form: https://forms.gle/PH6AH4xk9YF2TTKB7.\n  \n  H
 onors folks: feel free to submit your work for a chance to win prizes. All 
 are invited to swing by\, enter the raffle\, and vote for the Audience Favo
 rite!\n  \n  Email us at mura@cs.brown.edu with additional questions.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230428T151339Z
LOCATION:CIT\, Third Floor Atrium
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:The 8th Annual Brown CS Undergrad Research Symposium
TRANSP:OPAQUE
