 ed partner</a> to come up with 2 PLQ questions by 6pm\, and post it to the 
 PLQ Zulip channel. (If you can't make that schedule\, please let the HTAs k
 now ASAP.) Please use the template provided in the shared Google Drive <a h
 ref="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1SiltkQ-txsJ0UIok52SZF8kz_eFPt33Y7_1KE
 Nsp0Y4/edit">here</a>.
