DESCRIPTION:Deishacks is Brandeis University's Non-for-profit 48 hour Hacka
 thon! This year\, we have partnered with over 18 non-profits in our local W
 altham community and beyond. Students at Deishacks will decide which non-pr
 ofit speaks to them the most\, form teams\, and seek to solve a pain point 
 of their organization however they can. Teams will then present their minim
 um viable product to the judges of Deishacks. \n\nLearn more: deishacks.com
 \n\nWe hope to see you there!
